{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.1","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 5:1","prev_osis_id":"Mic.004.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.005.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Naissance et r\u00e8gne du Messie<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-5: cf. \u00c9s 9:5, 6. (Mt 2:1-11. Lu 2:1-14; 1:30-33.) Ps 72.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.5.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Et toi, Bethl\u00e9hem \u00c9phrata,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Petite entre les milliers de Juda,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">De toi sortira pour moi<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Celui qui dominera sur Isra\u00ebl,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et dont l\u2019origine remonte aux temps anciens,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Aux jours de l\u2019\u00e9ternit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.2","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.14","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.2","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 5:2","prev_osis_id":"Mic.005.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.005.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.5.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi il les livrera<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Jusqu\u2019au temps o\u00f9 enfantera celle qui doit enfanter,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et le reste de ses fr\u00e8res<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Reviendra aupr\u00e8s des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.3","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.3","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 5:3","prev_osis_id":"Mic.005.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.005.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.5.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Il se pr\u00e9sentera, et il gouvernera avec la force de l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Avec la majest\u00e9 du nom de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, son Dieu:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ils auront une demeure assur\u00e9e,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car il sera glorifi\u00e9 jusqu\u2019aux extr\u00e9mit\u00e9s de la terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.2","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.4","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 5:4","prev_osis_id":"Mic.005.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.005.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.5.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>C\u2019est lui qui ram\u00e8nera la paix.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Lorsque l\u2019Assyrien viendra dans notre pays,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et qu\u2019il p\u00e9n\u00e9trera dans nos palais,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Nous ferons lever contre lui sept pasteurs<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et huit princes du peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.3","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.5","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 5:5","prev_osis_id":"Mic.005.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.005.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.5.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ils feront avec l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e leur p\u00e2ture du pays d\u2019Assyrie<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et du pays de Nimrod au-dedans de ses portes.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il nous d\u00e9livrera ainsi de l\u2019Assyrien,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Lorsqu\u2019il viendra dans notre pays,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et qu\u2019il p\u00e9n\u00e9trera sur notre territoire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.6","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 5:6","prev_osis_id":"Mic.005.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.005.007,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 6-8: cf. Ro 11:11, 12, 15. \u00c9s 54:15-17. 2 Co 2:15, 16.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.5.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Le reste de Jacob sera au milieu des peuples nombreux<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Comme une ros\u00e9e qui vient de l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Comme des gouttes d\u2019eau sur l\u2019herbe:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elles ne comptent pas sur l\u2019homme,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elles ne d\u00e9pendent pas des enfants des hommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.7","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.7","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 5:7","prev_osis_id":"Mic.005.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.005.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.5.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Le reste de Jacob sera parmi les nations,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Au milieu des peuples nombreux,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Comme un lion parmi les b\u00eates de la for\u00eat,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Comme un lionceau parmi les troupeaux de brebis:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Lorsqu\u2019il passe, il foule et d\u00e9chire,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et personne ne d\u00e9livre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.8","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.8","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 5:8","prev_osis_id":"Mic.005.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.005.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.5.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Que ta main se l\u00e8ve sur tes adversaires,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et que tous tes ennemis soient extermin\u00e9s!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.9","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.7","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.9","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 5:9","prev_osis_id":"Mic.005.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.005.010,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 9-14: cf. Za 9:10; 13:2.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.5.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>En ce jour-l\u00e0, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">J\u2019exterminerai du milieu de toi tes chevaux,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et je d\u00e9truirai tes chars;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.10","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.8","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.10","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 5:10","prev_osis_id":"Mic.005.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.005.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.5.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>J\u2019exterminerai les villes de ton pays,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et je renverserai toutes tes forteresses;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.11","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.9","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.11","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 5:11","prev_osis_id":"Mic.005.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.005.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.5.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>J\u2019exterminerai de ta main les enchantements,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et tu n\u2019auras plus de magiciens;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.12","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.10","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.12","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 5:12","prev_osis_id":"Mic.005.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.005.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.5.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>J\u2019exterminerai du milieu de toi tes idoles et tes statues,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et tu ne te prosterneras plus devant l\u2019ouvrage de tes mains;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.13","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.11","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.13","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 5:13","prev_osis_id":"Mic.005.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.005.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.5.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>J\u2019exterminerai du milieu de toi tes idoles d\u2019Astart\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et je d\u00e9truirai tes villes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.14","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.12","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.14","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 5:14","prev_osis_id":"Mic.005.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.5.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>J\u2019exercerai ma vengeance avec col\u00e8re, avec fureur, sur les nations<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qui n\u2019ont pas \u00e9cout\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:1"